[DhtmlXQ_comment10_27]红优。[/DhtmlXQ_comment10_27]
[DhtmlXQ_comment11_27]红方亦略优。[/DhtmlXQ_comment11_27]
[DhtmlXQ_comment12_14]卒7进1，马四进六，红方具有强攻之势。[/DhtmlXQ_comment12_14]
[DhtmlXQ_comment12_15]红方抢占三线略优。[/DhtmlXQ_comment12_15]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13_13]红方以逸待劳，固防待变以俟在有利时机邀兑双车，则两头蛇将发挥重要作用。[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_13]
[DhtmlXQ_comment14_14]对抗之势。[/DhtmlXQ_comment14_14]
